metadata.name: Continuum
metadata.description:
Forward, backward…     
Northward, southward..     
Expand, recover…     
..recover, contract.     
     
We may always expand and never recover…     
…and through recovery, we may simply contract.     
   
The loss of perception,      
Realities through acceptance...     
Trial & error via inflection,     
Boundless cycles of inner repentance...     
    
We must continue on…     
…whether forward or backward…    
 …northward or southward…   
   
…we must continue on.
